videoSnippet.title: Parham Maghsoodloo is 2018 World Junior Champion With One Round to Spare | Performance 2900+
videoSnippet.description:
Follow me on Instagram for extra content: https://www.instagram.com/agadmator/

Check out the interview by Parham here https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hDh4INoGsQ0

Parham Maghsoodloo vs Maksim Vavulin
9/14/2018 Kocaeli - Gebze, World Junior Championship, Round 10
Sicilian Defense: Najdorf variaton (B90)

1. Nf3 c5 2. e4 d6 3. d4 Nf6 4. Nc3 cxd4 5. Nxd4 a6 6. h3 e5 7. Nde2 h5 8. Bg5 Be6 9. Bxf6 Qxf6 10. Nd5 Qd8 11. Qd3 g6 12. O-O-O Bh6+ 13. Kb1 Nd7 14. Qa3 Nc5 15. Nec3 O-O 16. h4 b5 17. f3 f5 18. Be2 Bg7 19. g4 hxg4 20. fxg4 fxg4 21. Rhg1 Rb8 22. Bxg4 Bf7 23. h5 gxh5 24. Bf5 Kh8 25. Ne2 Bh6 26. Qh3 Rg8 27. Rxg8+ Qxg8 28. Rg1 Qf8 29. Ng3 Rb7 30. Nf6 b4 31. Ngxh5 a5 32. Nh7 Bxa2+ 33. Kxa2 Rxh7 34. Bxh7 Kxh7 35. Qg4 Qf7+ 36. Kb1 Ne6 37. Nf6+
